subject: On Home page First and last name are separated by comma (,)
description:
Steps:
1. Login into Big Bang ASQ 2.0
2. Go to top-right corner of Home page 
3. First and last name are separated by comma (,)

Expected Result:
First and Last name must be separated by space

Actual Result:
First and last name are separated by comma (,)

subject: On Edit Profile page, First name, Last name zipcode and City can contain numbers and special characters
description:
Steps:
1. Go to Edit Profile page.
2. Enter numbers and special characters in First name, Last name and City .
3. Save Profile.

Expected Result:
User must  prompted an error indicating invalid zipcode and should not save.

Actual Result:
User can enter numbers and special characters in First name, Last name ,zipcode and City and save it.

Expected Result:

Actual Result:

subject: On change password page, Old Password and New Password can not be same.

subject: A user who is not even registered can click on forget password and can receive instructions
description:

3. Click Reset Password

Error message that the email is not a registered email

Actual :
The user who is not registered is able to  click on forget password
